<div class="about-container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Tarot.vn is a website specializing in Tarot readings, providing information and guidance on how to read and interpret Tarot cards.</p>
    <p>We believe that Tarot is a powerful tool to help people better understand themselves and their lives.</p>
    <p>We hope that the information and guidance on our website will help you better understand Tarot and how to use it to improve your life.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We are committed to providing accurate and useful information about Tarot, as well as creating a supportive community for sharing Tarot knowledge.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>We are a team of professionals passionate about Tarot, with many years of experience in this field.</p>
    <p>We are always ready to help and support you in better understanding Tarot and how to use it.</p>

    <h2>Online Tarot Reading for Finance</h2>
    <p>The financial Tarot reading feature on Tarot.vn will help you better understand your current financial situation and plan for the future. Our financial Tarot spreads provide suggestions and predictions about money management, helping you identify financial issues that need to be addressed as well as investment and savings opportunities. You'll receive helpful advice to improve your financial situation, from daily budget management to long-term investments, ensuring financial stability and growth in the future.</p>

    <h2>Online Tarot Reading for Career</h2>
    <p>Career Tarot readings on Tarot.vn provide deep insights into your career path. They help you identify opportunities and challenges in your current work and future prospects. The spreads include assessments of your current career status, upcoming professional opportunities, and strategies to achieve your career goals. Through detailed analysis, you can explore the necessary steps for career development, plan and shape your professional path. This helps improve work performance and prepare for changes in the work environment.</p>

    <h2>Tarot Reading for Health</h2>
    <p>The health Tarot reading feature on Tarot.vn provides predictions about potential health changes that may occur in the future. Health Tarot spreads help you assess your current physical and mental condition while identifying potential health issues. This feature not only helps you better prepare for health changes but also provides useful advice so you can actively protect and improve your health in the future.</p>

    <h2>Online Tarot Reading for Fortune</h2>
    <p>Fortune Tarot readings on Tarot.vn help you better understand how external factors influence your life. This feature provides spreads to explore future changes and trends based on your current fortune. Fortune spreads typically cover topics such as current fortune influences, predictions of upcoming changes, and strategies to take advantage of opportunities or deal with challenges. This feature helps you prepare for life's changes, allowing you to adjust your plans and decisions to achieve your future goals.</p>

    <h2>Our Tarot Reader Team</h2>
    <p>Our Reader team is not only well-versed in Tarot but also has broad knowledge in various life aspects such as love, career, finance, health, and more. With deep analytical skills and keen intuition, we will help you explore the depths of your issues and view things from different perspectives. Each Reader will listen carefully and understand your concerns, providing the most helpful solutions and advice. With the combination of analytical tools and guidance from Tarot experts, Tarot.vn is a valuable resource for seeking guidance and support in life.</p>

    <p>We greatly value all feedback and contributions from our user community to continuously improve and optimize the experience on Tarot.vn. Your suggestions and feedback will be an important motivation helping our team develop the website to be more complete and attractive. If you have any questions, suggestions, or comments, please leave a comment or contact us via the email below. We are always ready to listen and strive to best meet your needs.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For any feedback, you can contact us through:</p>
